SNMP NetApp cDot

Overview

For Netapp Ontape 9.5 and later.

Discovery rules:

  • Aggregates
  • Enclosures
  • LIFs
  • Nodes
  • SnapMirror (New)
  • Volumes

Based on “NETAPP ONTAP 9.1” edited by “zabbiJ”.
